aweme_list.desc: I’m glad we figured out what made her cry! 😂❤️ backstory ::: Kay started calling my name. I walked up and Kay was upset that Ellie had cried. I thought that was funny because Ellie cries every day, so I was confused why she was upset. She stated that this was different, because Ellie had a single tear fall! Ellie had never cried a tear before so this was a big deal! Apparently it was very sad to see, but just after, Ellie went right back to normal! 😂 Ellie was cooing and smiling when I talked to her, and it seemed like she wanted me to hold her. That’s when we decided that Ellie was probably just sad because she wanted me! 😂❤️ #kayandtayofficial #couples #relationships #pregnant #postpartum
